---
description: Keep app-domain logic in app repos and shared infrastructure in AppModules
alwaysApply: true
---

# Modules vs App Ownership Boundary

- App repos own domain behavior and app-specific contracts.
- `AppModules` owns reusable infrastructure primitives only.
- Do not place app-specific semantics in `AppModules`.
- Promote code to `AppModules` only when domain-agnostic and reusable across apps.
